resources.string: Airtel Payment Bank is a digital saving account in which you can do banking in mobile.It is similar as normal bank but its credit limit is less than the normal bank.

1) Interest rates:- 7.25% 

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- There is no charges in IMPS,UPI,NEFT etc

 4) You can withdraw cash in any Airtel Banking Point with some charges.

Paytm Payment Bank is a digital saving account in which you can do banking in mobile.It is similar as normal bank but its credit limit is only 1 lakh and if you deposit more than 1 lakh then money will deposit in Fixed Deposit.

1) Interest rates:- 4% 

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- There is no charges in IMPS,UPI,NEFT etc

 4) You can withdraw cash through debit card in any ATMs.

4) Offers cashback on Deposits of 25,000 into Paytm Payment Bank and get Rs 250(1 percent) upto 4 times.

5) Offers Phyical as well as Virtual Rupay Debit Card at Rs 120 and Anually Rs 100

Federal Bank offers Selfie, a mobile based SB account opening facility through Fedbook.It is a kind of Zero balance digital saving account by Federal.You can open a account through mobile with Aadhar and PAN card

1) Interest rates:- 4% on daily basis 

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- |-- There is no charges in UPI

 |-- It provides 4 free NEFT and IMPS transaction below 50,000 per month after that they will charge

 |-- Rs 300 Anually for Debit Card

 |-- There is no charge for Debit card Issuance

 4) ATM Debit card:- You will get a free ViSA EMV International Gold or Rupay Debit card.

5) Cheque book:- You will get a cheque book of 10 leaves per year free of cost.
Kotak Mahindra Bank offers a mobile based Zero Balance digital saving account with a virtual debit card for online shopping. You can open a account through mobile with Aadhar and PAN card
Icici Bank offers Zero balance digital saving account .You can open a account through mobile with Aadhar and PAN card

1) Interest rates:- Not mentioned yet

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- |-- There is no charges in UPI and Internet banking

 |-- It provides 4 free NEFT and IMPS transaction per month after that they will charge 90 rs for each transaction

 |-- No charge for Debit Card

 4) ATM Debit card:- You will get a free personalised Rupay Debit card.

5) Cheque book:- You will get a cheque book of 15 leaves per year free of cost.
Rbl Bank offers a digital Abacus Zero balance saving account .Its fastest, convenient and secured way of account opening online.You can open a account through mobile with Aadhar and PAN card

1) Interest rates:- Not mentioned 

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- |-- There is no charges in UPI

4) ATM Withdrawl:- Unlimited ATM Transaction.

5) Debit card:- You will get free phyical Debit card

Digi Bank offers a digital Zero balance digi saving account based on mobile.It is the India\'s first mobile onlt,paperless full bank that fits into your pocket.You can open a account through mobile with Aadhar and PAN card

1) Interest rates:- upto 7% 

2) Minimum balance:- Zero

3) Charges:- |-- There is no charges in UPI

 |-- Rs 150 Anually fee for Debit card

 |-- Rs 150 for Debit card replacement(Lost,Damaged,Stolen)

 |-- Rs 500 for Account closure(within 6 months of opening)

4) ATM Withdrawl:- Unlimited ATM withdrawal.
